<Turn speaker="spk7" startTime="4507.39" endTime="4884.925" fidelity="low">
<Sync time="4507.39"/>
No, pa, #eee, poglejmo, o čem bom danes govorila, torej, #eee, o točkovanju, 
<Sync time="4513.638"/>
#eee, besedil. 
<Sync time="4515.491"/>
